title: Jordan Central Bank Balance Sheet
description: Central Bank Balance Sheet in Jordan increased to 16648.90 JOD Million in September from 16404.13 JOD Million in August of 2022. Central Bank Balance Sheet in Jordan averaged 10184.22 JOD Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 17680 JOD Million in December of 2021 and a record low of 4246.50 JOD Million in December of 2001. This page provides - Jordan Central Bank Balance Sheet- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Jordan
